message.body: Hey. Me and Eden stopped at the house. We're playing with Bu a bit. I put the mail on the furniture near the door
Ok did he have food and water??
I think I left a wet rag lying around somewhere. It was one of my white ones. We meant to take it with us. We used it to clean Bu's eye crusties.
I didn't see one anyone but I wasn't looking ill check when I get home. No big deal
Okay. It's either in the back room, living room, or basement near my stuff. Can you throw it in the dirty clothes.
